{
  "texts": [
    "By defining and communicating specific usage policies, organisations could limit potentially harmful uses of the LLM.",
    "This could also be used to then inform real-time monitoring and oversight of the LLM.",
    "Real-time monitoring means that problematic uses or responses from the LLM are flagged and handled appropriately, and it can inform preventative training of employees.",
    "Using sentiment analysis of the recorded prompts and outputs could also identify discriminatory or hateful speech, contributing to a more ethical system.",
    "Actuaries' Code"
  ]
}